4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, and network administration, alongside practical cybersecurity techniques like cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course materials are available in both English and Spanish, with live instruction in the campus' language. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop